text: Clara Bimbocci (born 16 April 1919) was an Italian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lucca
